"节点内存使用率异常飙升，node_memory_usage_rate从32.29%上升到51.91%（变化率46.6%），可用内存从11GB减少到7.7GB\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 32.29% → 51.91% (变化率46.6%), node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 11,002,662,912 → 7,720,468,480 bytes\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从4394ms飙升到4703ms，P99值从10301.6ms激增至90984.28ms（变化率159.32%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 4394ms → 4703ms, P99: 10301.6ms → 90984.28ms (变化率159.32%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"错误率异常，client_error_ratio和error_ratio的P99值从0%激增至19.55%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio P99: 0% → 19.55%, error_ratio P99: 0% → 19.55%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **主要故障模式**：节点级内存资源瓶颈\n   - `aiops-k8s-04` 节点内存使用率从32.29%飙升到51.91%（变化率46.6%）\n   - 可用内存从11GB减少到7.7GB，降幅达35%\n\n2. **服务级影响**：\n   - `currencyservice-1` 响应时间P99值激增159.32%，达到90秒\n   - `cartservice-1` 错误率P99值达到19.55%\n   - 多个服务的`rrt_max`指标出现异常\n\n3. **节点-服务关联**：\n   - `aiops-k8s-04` 节点上运行着 `checkoutservice-0`, `frontend-2`, `currencyservice-1`\n   - 内存压力可能导致这些服务性能下降\n\n这看起来是一个典型的节点资源瓶颈导致的级联故障，需要进一步分析日志和追踪数据来确认具体原因。\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n根据收集到的追踪数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **延迟指标 (`rrt_max`)**:\n   - `checkoutservice->checkoutservice`: 多个操作（如 `EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation`、`ShippingService/GetQuote`、`PaymentService/Charge`）的延迟显著增加，延迟倍数在 3.3 到 4.9 倍之间。\n   - `frontend->frontend`: `AdService/GetAds` 操作的延迟从 5549.49 增加到 41472.57，延迟倍数约为 7.5 倍。\n   - `frontend->productcatalogservice`: `ListProducts` 操作的延迟从 72.73 增加到 224.08，延迟倍数约为 3.1 倍。\n\n2. **错误状态 (`error_ratio`)**:\n   - `frontend->frontend`: `AdService/GetAds` 操作出现 `context deadline exceeded` 错误（状态码 4），表明请求超时。\n\n3. **调用关系**:\n   - `checkoutservice->checkoutservice` 是主要的延迟和错误传播路径。\n   - `frontend->frontend` 和 `frontend->productcatalogservice` 也存在延迟问题。\n\n### 假设\n- **根因组件**: `checkoutservice` 是主要的延迟和错误传播点。\n- **原因**: 多个下游操作（如 `EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation`、`ShippingService/GetQuote`、`PaymentService/Charge`）的延迟显著增加，导致整体性能下降。\n- **证据**: 延迟倍数显著增加（3.3 到 4.9 倍），且 `frontend->frontend` 的超时错误可能是由 `checkoutservice` 的延迟间接引起的。\n\n### 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->frontend\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个操作的延迟显著增加（3.3 到 4.9 倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService/GetAds 操作出现 context deadline exceeded 错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n================================\n请基于上述全量信息以及你的 Trace 数据，对当前故障进行分析。\n重点：请在返回 JSON 的 'stance' 字段中明确标记 'SUPPORT', 'OPPOSE' 或 'NEUTRAL'。", "raw_metric_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载metric数据。UUID: ff15d32c-199", "anomaly_metrics": "metric_type,service_name,pod_name,node_name,metric_name,normal_median,fault_median,normal_p99,fault_p99,median_change_ratio,p99_change_ratio\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-1,N/A,client_error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.0,19.55,0.0,2.0\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-1,N/A,error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.0,19.55,0.0,2.0\nservice,currencyservice,currencyservice-1,N/A,rrt_max,4394.0,4703.0,10301.6,90984.28,0.0679,1.5932\nservice,adservice,adservice-0,N/A,rrt_max,42993.0,10244.0,49259.8,34025.0,1.2303,0.3658\nservice,currencyservice,currencyservice-0,N/A,rrt_max,4061.0,3592.0,35804.16,9447.64,0.1226,1.1649\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-0,N/A,rrt_max,3429.0,3067.0,40398.6,15263.36,0.1115,0.9031\npod,N/A,redis-cart-0,N/A,pod_cpu_usage,0.0,0.0,0.12,0.05,0.0,0.7576\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-0,N/A,r